:3045644,\"anonymousAuthor\":null,\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"interactions\":{\"vote\":null},\"excludedPermissions\":[\"vote\",\"accept\",\"reject\",\"mark_spam\",\"integrate\",\"archive\",\"destroy\"],\"permissions\":[]},\"votesTotal\":35,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"id\":4049010,\"hasVoters\":true,\"createdAt\":1474409750,\"commentableType\":\"Annotation\",\"commentableId\":3489810,\"body\":{\"markdown\":\"This is like the grown-up and more radio friendly version of \\\"Where I\'m From\\\" off of In My Lifetime.\",\"html\":\"<p>This is like the grown-up and more radio friendly version of “Where I’m From” off of In My Lifetime.<\/p>\"},\"apiPath\":\"/comments/4049010\",\"type\":\"comment\"}},\"annotations\":{\"3489810\":{\"verifiedBy\":null,\"topComment\":4049010,\"rejectionComment\":null,\"createdBy\":2,\"cosignedBy\":[],\"authors\":[{\"user\":1729630,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"attribution\":0.5538461538461539,\"type\":\"user_attribution\"},{\"user\":2,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"attribution\":0.2,\"type\":\"user_attribution\"},{\"user\":5773568,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"attribution\":0.07692307692307693,\"type\":\"user_attribution\"},{\"user\":12978,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"attribution\":0.05384615384615385,\"type\":\"user_attribution\"},{\"user\":7,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"attribution\":0.038461538461538464,\"type\":\"user_attribution\"},{\"user\":1043822,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"attribution\":0.038461538461538464,\"type\":\"user_attribution\"},{\"user\":2701698,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"attribution\":0.023076923076923075,\"type\":\"user_attribution\"},{\"user\":149650,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"attribution\":0.015384615384615385,\"type\":\"user_attribution\"}],\"acceptedBy\":12,\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"iqByAction\":{},\"interactions\":{\"vote\":null,\"pyong\":false,\"cosign\":false},\"excludedPermissions\":[\"vote\",\"edit\",\"cosign\",\"uncosign\",\"destroy\",\"accept\",\"reject\",\"see_unreviewed\",\"clear_votes\",\"propose_edit_to\",\"pin_to_profile\",\"unpin_from_profile\",\"update_source\",\"edit_custom_preview\",\"create_comment\"],\"permissions\":[]},\"votesTotal\":203,\"verified\":false,\"url\":\"https://genius.com/3489810/Jay-z-empire-state-of-mind/Empire-state-of-mind\",\"twitterShareMessage\":\"“The Blueprint 3’s third single is a love song to Jay-Z and Alicia Keys\' home city of New York, which is …” —@Genius\",\"state\":\"accepted\",\"source\":null,\"shareUrl\":\"https://genius.com/3489810\",\"referentId\":3489810,\"pyongsCount\":1,\"proposedEditCount\":0,\"pinned\":false,\"needsExegesis\":false,\"id\":3489810,\"hasVoters\":true,\"embedContent\":\"<blockquote class=\'rg_standalone_container\' data-src=\'//genius.com/annotations/3489810/standalone_embed\'><a href=\'https://genius.com/3489810/Jay-z-empire-state-of-mind/Empire-state-of-mind\'>Empire State of Mind<\/a><br><a href=\'https://genius.com/Jay-z-empire-state-of-mind-lyrics\'>&#8213; JAY-Z (Ft. Alicia Keys) – Empire State of Mind<\/a><\/blockquote><script async crossorigin src=\'//genius.com/annotations/load_standalone_embeds.js\'><\/script>\",\"deleted\":false,\"customPreview\":null,\"createdAt\":1253653325,\"community\":true,\"commentCount\":1,\"body\":{\"markdown\":\"*The Blueprint 3*\'s third single is a love song to Jay-Z and Alicia Keys\' home city of New York, which is also known as \\\"the Empire State.\\\" The title alludes to the [Billy Joel](/artists/Billy-joel) ballad, [\\\"New York State of Mind,\\\"](http://rock.rapgenius.com/Billy-joel-new-york-state-of-mind-lyrics) and [Nas](/artists/Nas)\' [\\\"N.Y. State of Mind.\\\"](https://genius.com/Nas-ny-state-of-mind-lyrics)\\n\\n\\\"Empire State of Mind\\\" stands as one of Hov\'s most successful singles. It was the first Jay-Z-lead single to ever top the *Billboard* \\\"Hot 100,\\\" sitting at #1 for five consecutive weeks (also being the last number #1 in the 2000s). It has been certified 5x Multi-Platinum by the *RIAA* for sales of over 5.5 million in the United States. The track was nominated for three Grammy Awards, winning \\\"Best Rap Song\\\" and \\\"Best Rap/Sung Collaboration.\\\"\",\"html\":\"<p><em>The Blueprint 3<\/em>’s third single is a love song to Jay-Z and Alicia Keys\' home city of New York, which is also known as “the Empire State.” The title alludes to the <a href=\\\"https://genius.com/artists/Billy-joel\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" data-api_path=\\\"/artists/16965\\\">Billy Joel<\/a> ballad, <a href=\\\"http://rock.genius.com/Billy-joel-new-york-state-of-mind-lyrics\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" data-api_path=\\\"/songs/195634\\\">“New York State of Mind,”<\/a> and <a href=\\\"https://genius.com/artists/Nas\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" data-api_path=\\\"/artists/56\\\">Nas<\/a>‘ <a href=\\\"https://genius.com/Nas-ny-state-of-mind-lyrics\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" data-api_path=\\\"/songs/89\\\">“N.Y. State of Mind.”<\/a><\/p>\\n\\n<p>“Empire State of Mind” stands as one of Hov’s most successful singles. It was the first Jay-Z-lead single to ever top the <em>Billboard<\/em> “Hot 100,” sitting at #1 for five consecutive weeks (also being the last number #1 in the 2000s). It has been certified 5x Multi-Platinum by the <em>RIAA<\/em> for sales of over 5.5 million in the United States. The track was nominated for three Grammy Awards, winning “Best Rap Song” and “Best Rap/Sung Collaboration.”<\/p>\"},\"beingCreated\":false,\"apiPath\":\"/annotations/3489810\",\"type\":\"annotation\"}},\"referents\":{\"2622\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":2622},\"2626\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":2626},\"2630\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":2630},\"2634\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":2634},\"2635\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":2635},\"2636\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":2636},\"2676\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":2676},\"3585\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":3585},\"3669\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":3669},\"3679\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":3679},\"3682\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":3682},\"5903\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":5903},\"5910\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":5910},\"5912\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":5912},\"5913\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":5913},\"5915\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":5915},\"5980\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":5980},\"5982\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":5982},\"12596\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":12596},\"16343\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":16343},\"16345\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":16345},\"17592\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":17592},\"27083\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":27083},\"42854\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":42854},\"48735\":{\"classification\":\"verified\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":48735},\"62654\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":62654},\"192026\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":192026},\"197461\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":197461},\"226160\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editorialState\":\"accepted\",\"id\":226160},\"241513\":{\"classification\":\"accepted\",\"editor